      &lt;img alt="AT&amp;amp;amp;T logo with an illustrated red and orange background." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/B9EtIdFtKXi1flfeBB72_sjF2SI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73761941/STK158_ATT_02.0.jpg" /&gt;
